org.onehippo.forge.jcrrunner

Interface RunnerPlugin

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractRunnerPlugin, FolderConverterPlugin, LoggingPlugin

    public interface RunnerPlugin
    All RunnerPlugins must implement this interface directly or extend the AbstractRunnerPlugin.
